"2019-01-29T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"真係慘個班婆婆從來唔會問人攞錢。佢地都係有骨氣情願執成日得十幾蚊都唔會去求人。就算人地比佢佢地都會拒絕。"},{"pid":"887c411601b54663fb2cb13c52a92aece3c11ffd","tid":999604,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"恰老人家呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370f93c91cc26b7005a796a964a07f001bec8f95","tid":999604,"uid":179283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:10:31.000Z","msg":"俾啲假鈔佢 等佢用果陣俾人捉到坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6e9023f20c6ca467a92103fe7bec4d6e6ae0ed","tid":999604,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5417265ab5bfc5f88f574d3b983cc0a398a62dbd","tid":999604,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"370f93c91cc26b7005a796a964a07f001bec8f95","tid":999604,"uid":179283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:10:31.000Z","msg":"俾啲假鈔佢 等佢用果陣俾人捉到坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T09:33:46.000Z","msg":"好主意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}